#: ../../config.rst:175
msgid ""
"This section is cache backend related settings used by vstutils-based "
"application. vstutils supports all cache backends that Django does. "
"Filesystem, in-memory, memcached are supported out of the box and many "
"others are supported with additional plugins. You can find details about "
